Let me analyze the target image and provide a detailed solution.

Analysis of the Main Target Image:
The image shows two structures:
1. Left Structure:
- Has two blue cubes on top
- A green horizontal block below
- A red block with semicircle cutout
- Yellow base block
- Orange triangular block on the side

2. Right Structure (taller):
- Orange triangular block on top
- Yellow horizontal block
- Two green vertical blocks
- Yellow horizontal block
- Red block with circular cutout
- Yellow base block

The structure uses multiple layers and various block types including cubes, rectangular blocks, blocks with cutouts, and triangular blocks.

Required blocks from dictionary with indices:
- Blue cubes (index 4)
- Green vertical blocks (index 7)
- Green horizontal block (index 6)
- Red blocks with cutouts (indices 1, 2)
- Yellow horizontal blocks (indices 8, 9)
- Yellow vertical blocks (indices 10, 11)
- Orange triangular blocks (indices 13, 14, 15, or 16)

Assembly Order:
For both structures, we build from bottom up:

{
Step1: Move block with index 8 (yellow horizontal base - left structure)
Step2: Move block with index 2 (red block with cutout - left structure)
Step3: Move block with index 6 (green horizontal block - left structure)
Step4: Move block with index 4 (blue cube - left structure front)
Step5: Move block with index 4 (blue cube - left structure back)
Step6: Move block with index 14 (orange triangle - left structure side)
Step7: Move block with index 8 (yellow horizontal base - right structure)
Step8: Move block with index 1 (red block with circular cutout - right structure)
Step9: Move block with index 8 (yellow horizontal block - right structure middle)
Step10: Move block with index 7 (green vertical block - right structure front)
Step11: Move block with index 7 (green vertical block - right structure back)
Step12: Move block with index 8 (yellow horizontal block - right structure top)
Step13: Move block with index 14 (orange triangle - right structure top)
}
